<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بِمَا يُنَاسِبهَا مِمَّا يُوجب الْحَد فتعزير مُقَدمَات الزِّنَا الَّتِي لَا توجب الْحَد تنقص عَن الزِّنَا لَا عَن حد الشّرْب مثلا وَهَكَذَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَو عَفا مُسْتَحقّ حد<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنهُ كَحَد قذف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَلَا تَعْزِير للْإِمَام فِي الْأَصَح<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمُقَابِله لَهُ التَّعْزِير<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَو<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَفا مُسْتَحقّ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَعْزِير<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
