<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>وَمُقَابِله يجب الدّفع<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>وَالدَّفْع عَن<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
