<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>وَهِي الْإِنَاء من الفخار<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>وَلم تنْدَفع عَنهُ إِلَّا بِكَسْرِهَا<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
